00:30:37,210 --> 00:30:39,963
Even if I saw it, I'd be able to make excuses like I do now.

267
00:30:40,046 --> 00:30:42,590
-(Fuyu) That's not your intention... -(Yukiya) Well, tell me.

268
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:47,136
Where were you with him today?

269
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:48,638
(Fuyu) That's...

270
00:30:48,721 --> 00:30:52,600
Why... were you in that town?

271
00:30:59,816 --> 00:31:03,528
I don't know, I don't know anything

272
00:31:05,822 --> 00:31:06,948
Really?

273
00:31:08,408 --> 00:31:09,242
yes

274
00:31:13,496 --> 00:31:15,623
Aren't you hiding something?

275
00:31:17,083 --> 00:31:17,917
yes

276
00:31:23,965 --> 00:31:25,049
I see.

277
00:31:28,845 --> 00:31:29,887
oh dear…

278
00:31:33,057 --> 00:31:34,434
That's right, isn't it?

279
00:31:36,894 --> 00:31:41,065
you can't say anything anyway

280
00:31:43,026 --> 00:31:47,947
After all, he is a servant of the Ise family.

281
00:31:52,201 --> 00:31:54,913
you may not betray me

282
00:31:55,788 --> 00:31:57,957
Maybe I won't bully you

283
00:32:01,210 --> 00:32:02,045
but…

284
00:32:08,801 --> 00:32:10,470
not on your side

285
00:32:24,442 --> 00:32:26,361
After losing my mother⸺

286
00:32:27,111 --> 00:32:32,492
I think it's true that I was also a child and wanted it.

287
00:32:33,284 --> 00:32:37,330
someone who can take the place of a mother

288
00:32:42,543 --> 00:32:44,087
For me back then⸺

289
00:32:46,339 --> 00:32:49,425
I couldn't think of anyone but you

290
00:32:54,931 --> 00:32:58,977
I didn't notice it until this year...

291
00:33:03,147 --> 00:33:04,232
I wonder what it is

292
00:33:06,109 --> 00:33:08,528
Maybe it was because I had the lid on.

293
00:33:16,786 --> 00:33:18,538
I didn't want to notice

294
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:29,549
You have been so far⸺

295
00:33:32,885 --> 00:33:37,140
He never once sacrificed his body to protect me.

296
00:34:20,892 --> 00:34:22,310
(Reo) Yukiya

297
00:34:22,393 --> 00:34:24,145
Ah... Huh?

298
00:34:24,771 --> 00:34:27,440
-(Reo) What's wrong? -(Yukiya) Oh no...

299
00:34:27,523 --> 00:34:28,941
I was in a daze though

300
00:34:30,109 --> 00:34:32,361
No, it's nothing.

301
00:34:33,029 --> 00:34:34,405
(Reo) That's good.

302
00:34:39,619 --> 00:34:40,620
thank you

303
00:35:25,581 --> 00:35:29,293
Yukiya-san, this is OK. Is there anything I can help you with?

304
00:35:29,794 --> 00:35:32,380
It's okay because it seems like it's over now too

305
00:35:32,463 --> 00:35:33,631
Thank you for your hard work

306
00:35:35,007 --> 00:35:36,384
(Reo) Thank you for your hard work.

307
00:35:37,176 --> 00:35:40,346
Yukiya-san, do you have time after this?

308
00:35:40,429 --> 00:35:41,347
Huh?

309
00:35:41,430 --> 00:35:42,557
(Reo) Something...

310
00:35:43,141 --> 00:35:47,144
I would like to talk to you again about the future.

311
00:35:47,979 --> 00:35:50,523
Ah... nice

312
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:52,984
I've never gone out drinking.

313
00:35:53,067 --> 00:35:53,943
(Reo) I did it

314
00:35:54,443 --> 00:35:56,154
I found a nice store across the street⸺

315
00:35:56,237 --> 00:35:57,446
How about it there?

316
00:35:57,530 --> 00:36:00,533
(Yukiya) Okay, I'll just make sure the door is locked.

317
00:36:00,616 --> 00:36:01,492
yes

318
00:36:23,598 --> 00:36:26,058
-(Reo) Huh? -(Yukiya) Yeah?

319
00:36:26,142 --> 00:36:28,019
I think I got lost somehow.

320
00:36:28,102 --> 00:36:29,770
Ah... not at all

321
00:36:29,854 --> 00:36:30,855
Sorry

322
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:37,195
(Male) Yukiya Ise

323
00:36:37,278 --> 00:36:40,448
9:19 p.m. Arrested on suspicion of violating the Specified Secrets Protection Act

324
00:36:40,531 --> 00:36:41,365
Huh?

325
00:36:43,993 --> 00:36:45,745
-(Yukiya) Huh? -(Male) Come on.

326
00:36:48,915 --> 00:36:50,791
(Yukiya) Ngh... Shit!

327
00:37:09,727 --> 00:37:11,520
It's my own fault

328
00:37:14,023 --> 00:37:16,025
♪～

329
00:37:17,610 --> 00:37:22,073
Yukiya was the one who used me first.

330
00:38:10,830 --> 00:38:12,832
～♪

331
00:38:13,582 --> 00:38:14,750
(Yukiya) What do you mean?

332
00:38:14,834 --> 00:38:17,253
Don't interfere with my happiness anymore

333
00:38:17,336 --> 00:38:20,339
(Yukiya) I will never forgive you

334
00:38:20,423 --> 00:38:22,133
(Erika) I can't believe we're trying to kill you⸺

335
00:38:22,216 --> 00:38:24,010
That's impossible, right?

336
00:38:24,093 --> 00:38:25,136
 (Seiichiro) No matter what happens⸺

337
00:38:25,219 --> 00:38:27,805
Don't overturn those words
